<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/subject/authors_section.6022b.css">

<h2>
    
  

  <h2>
    <span>浮生六记的创作者</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


</h2>
<div class="indent">
    <p></p>
    <div id="authors" class="authors">
    <ul class="authors-list from-subject __oneline">
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4546904/" title="沈复">
                    <img src="https://img9.doubanio.com/img/author/raw/public/1495858653.75.jpg" alt="沈复" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4546904/" title="沈复" class="name">沈复</a>
                    <span class="role">作者</span>
                </div>
            </li>
             
        <li class="author fake fake5"></li>
    </ul>
    </div>
</div>

  




  


  


  


  


    
  

  <h2>
    <span>作者简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



      <div class="indent ">
          
            <div class="">
            <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>沈复（1763~？），字三白，号梅逸，江苏苏州人。年轻时秉承父业，以游幕经商为生，后偕妻离家别居，妻子客死扬州。46岁时有感于“苏东坡云‘事如春梦了无痕’，苟不记之笔墨，未免有辜彼苍之厚”，乃作《浮生六记》。</p></div>

            </div>
      </div>

  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  





  

  
    




  

